cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GT 

This paper deals with scene representation and manipulation using deep generative models, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The paper also involves disentangled representations and deep learning, which are relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the manipulation of 3D scenes, which is related to computational geometry (cs.GT).
